{"tid":1029323,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街街市4食客瑣事嘈交 互毆俱傷","createTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T15:54:31.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b13ea7b28424ce3f080115dbac339e08c35b93c1","tid":1029323,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190125/large/1548431895_a076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190125%2Flarge%2F1548431895_a076.jpg&h=b79e2202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4名男子於瑞和街食肆互毆，同告受傷送院。(姜偉康攝)<br />\n<br />\n觀塘瑞和街街市，周五晚上11時許，兩名男子於街市4樓一間食肆用膳期間，疑因瑣事與另外兩名男食客爭執，初則口角繼而動武，職員見狀報案。警員接報到場，4名男子均報稱受傷，一併由救護車送院治理。警方正封鎖現場調查。"},{"pid":"f88e2eaef0757c48ef4a6102ca2c63b038389fe3","tid":1029323,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"@世清"},{"pid":"c5990f6a38b495a24a3e7fed4a19c31bd14e3d26","tid":1029323,"uid":67252,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:09:48.000Z","msg":"先生，篤痰係你吐架？"},{"pid":"921c49fa359f638c0430b800253201aa5b5cff94","tid":1029323,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88e2eaef0757c48ef4a6102ca2c63b038389fe3","tid":1029323,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"@世清"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"世清唔打交"},{"pid":"d6e60b23d3e1b99fa21e288a470f6786ca3da8e2","tid":1029323,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"921c49fa359f638c0430b800253201aa5b5cff94","tid":1029323,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88e2eaef0757c48ef4a6102ca2c63b038389fe3","tid":1029323,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"@世清"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"世清唔打交"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07: